32#ifndef _I915DRM_I915_PCI_H_
33#define _I915DRM_I915_PCI_H_
34
35#include <sys/queue.h>
36#include <sys/workqueue.h>
37
38struct i915drmkms_task {
39 union {
40 SIMPLEQ_ENTRY(i915drmkms_task) queue;
41 struct work work;
42 } ift_u;
43 void (*ift_fn)(struct i915drmkms_task *);
44};
45
46static inline void
47i915drmkms_task_init(struct i915drmkms_task *task,
48 void (*fn)(struct i915drmkms_task *))
49{
50
51 task->ift_fn = fn;
52}
53
54int i915drmkms_task_schedule(device_t, struct i915drmkms_task *);
55
56#endif /* _I915DRM_I915_PCI_H_ */
